desc: Elina specializes in private personal pilates training and semi-private sessions that aim for full body well being. From proper breathing, postural alignment, and activity patterns your personally designed workout will build strength, coordination, flexibility, and ease of movement.

layout.text: Align Your Posture, Align Your Life

Elina brings ALL of her experiences to you ~ from Figure Skating, Weight Training, Dance & Pilates ~ A culmination of her studies in a desire to create the very best YOU ~ Let's Connect to create a program that you will not only LOVE but ENJOY
